---
title: Sweet and Sour Chicken with Pineapple and Peppers over Jasmine Rice
description: Sweet and sour may be a Chinese takeout staple, but our DIY version is proof that some things are even better when made at home (and totally worth the effort). That’s because there’s less grease and more veggies in it, so it feels lighter and tastes brighter, too. There’s even some bonus pineapple thrown into the mix of chicken and peppers to ensure that you get plenty of sweet, sweet satisfaction.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-and-sour-chicken-5f547a93.jpg
